initialize proxy - no Session\n\tat java.base/java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:1595)\nCaused by: java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\n\tat java.base/java.lang.reflect.Method.invoke(Method.java:586)\nCaused by: org.hibernate.LazyInitializationException: failed to lazily initialize a collection of role: org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.cargo.Cargo.itinerary.legs: could not initialize proxy - no Session\n\tat java.base/java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:1595)\nCaused by: java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\n\tat java.base/java.lang.reflect.Method.invoke(Method.java:586)\nCaused by: org.hibernate.LazyInitializationException: failed to lazily initialize a collection of role: org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.cargo.Cargo.itinerary.legs: could not initialize proxy - no Session\n\tat java.base/java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:1595)\nCaused by: java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"83d9035c-c20b-4877-bffd-f348c2f149e2","uuid":"bf74d2fc-ae11-4cba-92f2-6369bcd4e498"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_018EhJ8Mj6MCU5J8iLGu8Mmg","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Found it. The root cause is `LazyInitializationException: failed to lazily initialize a collection of role: org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.cargo.Cargo.itinerary.legs: could not initialize proxy - no Session`. \n\nThis is a classic JPA issue - the `legs` collection inside `Itinerary` is lazily loaded, but when the `toDto` method tries to access it, the persistence session/transaction is no longer active. In Quarkus with Panache, this was handled differently.\n\nI need to fix the `JpaCargoRepository.listAll()` to eagerly fetch the itinerary legs, or add a `@Transactional` annotation to the service layer. Let me check the current state of the repository."}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1083,"cache_read_input_tokens":66329,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1083,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":422},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"83d9035c-c20b-4877-bffd-f348c2f149e2","uuid":"eb65e1ba-fe49-468b-bfde-0023dbf12e29"}
