{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01S2kd1QShYMn26fJsWJSUZH","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Two issues to fix:\n\n1. **LazyInitializationException**: The `listAll()` query in `JpaCargoRepository` does a simple `SELECT c FROM Cargo c`, but the `itinerary.legs` collection is lazily loaded. By the time `CargoRouteDtoAssembler.toDto()` accesses it, the JPA session is closed. I need to use a `JOIN FETCH` to eagerly load the legs.\n\n2. **Event logger 404**: The smoke test tries `/event-logger.xhtml` but the actual path is `/event-logger/index.xhtml`.\n\nLet me fix both issues:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":640,"cache_read_input_tokens":71390,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":640,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":409},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"83d9035c-c20b-4877-bffd-f348c2f149e2","uuid":"ecd29fd2-6a20-4998-975c-b01d1947899a"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01S2kd1QShYMn26fJsWJSUZH","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01XX3mjMNWKfrDzWCNPgdexn","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaCargoRepository.java","old_string":"  public List<Cargo> listAll() {\n    return entityManager.createQuery(\"SELECT c FROM Cargo c\", Cargo.class).getResultList();\n  }","new_string":"  public List<Cargo> listAll() {\n    return entityManager.createQuery(\n        \"SELECT DISTINCT c FROM Cargo c LEFT JOIN FETCH c.itinerary.legs\", Cargo.class)\n        .getResultList();\n  }"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":640,"cache_read_input_tokens":71390,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":640,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":409},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"83d9035c-c20b-4877-bffd-f348c2f149e2","uuid":"ecfafbed-893a-433c-9bb9-121b647d1e2f"}
