{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Kg7KEPrgNAZCc19nGZZJdY","type":"tool_result","content":"*   Trying ::1:8080...\n* Connected to localhost (::1) port 8080 (#0)\n> GET /cargo-tracker/rest/graph-traversal/shortest-path?origin=CNHKG&destination=SESTO HTTP/1.1\r\n> Host: localhost:8080\r\n> User-Agent: curl/7.76.1\r\n> Accept: application/json\r\n> \r\n* Mark bundle as not supporting multiuse\n< HTTP/1.1 200 OK\r\n< Content-Type: application/json\r\n< Content-Language: en-US\r\n< Content-Length: 117\r\n< Date: Sat, 14 Mar 2026 13:57:20 GMT\r\n< \r\n{ [117 bytes data]\n* Connection #0 to host localhost left intact\n{\"transitPaths\":[{\"transitEdges\":[{\"voyageNumber\":\"0100S\",\"fromUnLocode\":\"CNHKG\",\"toUnLocode\":\"USCHI\",\"fromDate\"}]}]}","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"83d9035c-c20b-4877-bffd-f348c2f149e2","uuid":"0a392185-a242-48f1-8a5d-7b1caa0a96a1"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01BPUp7npnaDbv5APmUeBg2H","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Content-Length says 117 bytes, and the response is indeed 117 bytes - so it's returning complete but with malformed JSON. The `fromDate` field has no value. This means JSON-B is serializing `LocalDateTime` but producing invalid output.\n\nThe issue is likely that JSON-B in Open Liberty writes the field name `\"fromDate\"` but then encounters a `LocalDateTime` that it can't serialize to a simple type, producing nothing after the field name.\n\nThe fix is to register a `LocalDateTime` adapter. Let me check if there's a `RestConfiguration`:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":377,"cache_read_input_tokens":134329,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":377,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":228},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"83d9035c-c20b-4877-bffd-f348c2f149e2","uuid":"0d5d76b2-3653-4026-9cd9-6dc3f3821753"}
