{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01EPoWEU9espJsxiSG9ANLuR","type":"tool_result","content":"    80→  private Itinerary toItinerary(TransitPath transitPath) {\n    81→    List<Leg> legs =\n    82→        transitPath.getTransitEdges().stream().map(this::toLeg).collect(Collectors.toList());\n    83→    return new Itinerary(legs);\n    84→  }\n    85→\n    86→  private Leg toLeg(TransitEdge edge) {\n    87→    return new Leg(\n    88→        voyageRepository.find(new VoyageNumber(edge.getVoyageNumber())),\n    89→        locationRepository.find(new UnLocode(edge.getFromUnLocode())),\n    90→        locationRepository.find(new UnLocode(edge.getToUnLocode())),\n    91→        edge.getFromDate(),\n    92→        edge.getToDate());\n    93→  }\n    94→}\n    95→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"83d9035c-c20b-4877-bffd-f348c2f149e2","uuid":"77b71fa7-ff64-48b7-a784-7dec9054ab0b"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01J1HRY7GQbmyRBtfTLNyqW7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `ExternalRoutingService.toLeg()` uses `getFromDate()/getToDate()` as `LocalDateTime`. But the `ExternalRoutingService` calls the REST API and deserializes the JSON response - so it goes through JSON serialization/deserialization round-trip.\n\nThe cleanest approach since JSON-B isn't handling `LocalDateTime` on Open Liberty: change the type to `String` in the REST DTO and convert appropriately. But that's a bigger change. Let me try another approach - register the Jackson JAX-RS provider instead, since we have Jackson in our dependencies:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":480,"cache_read_input_tokens":144018,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":480,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":260},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"83d9035c-c20b-4877-bffd-f348c2f149e2","uuid":"729907a6-fe0d-4042-8f2e-89019ced30a4"}
